title: Features & Benefits of a K&N Air Intake on 2010-2012 Mazda 3 Mazdaspeed 2.3L
description: Find out just what kind of performance gains you can expect with a K&N Air Intake (part # K&N 69-6012TS) on your 2010-2012 Mazda 3 Mazdaspeed.

asset.title: 2010-2012 Mazda 3 Mazdaspeed 2.3L Air Intake Feature Promo Video
asset.description:
Performance cold air intake by K&N for 2010-2012 Mazda 3 Mazdaspeed 2.3L

http://www.knfilters.com/search/product.aspx?prod=69-6012TS

K&N dynamometer tests show an estimated 24.22 horsepower gain at 5000 RPM with use of this K&N air intake modification.

K&N 69-6012TS fits the following: 
2013 MAZDA MAZDASPEED3 2.3L 
2012 MAZDA MAZDASPEED3 2.3L 
2011 MAZDA MAZDASPEED3 2.3L 
2010 MAZDA MAZDASPEED3 2.3L
